WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:27.400
 The year 1144 of the Age of Exiles, Hound Moon.

00:00:27.400 --> 00:00:33.000
 There it is fell through the night air, waitless.

00:00:33.000 --> 00:00:36.200
 He caught glimpses of the tower of Brickhan.

00:00:36.200 --> 00:00:41.960
 Caledus is still smoldering outline at the window, then below, the river coming up to meet him.

00:00:41.960 --> 00:00:46.520
 He slammed into the water, the cold shocking the breath out of him.

00:00:46.520 --> 00:00:51.520
 He panicked, disorientated, realizing he didn't know which way was up.

00:00:51.520 --> 00:00:54.280
 All about him was darkness and ice.

00:00:54.280 --> 00:01:00.880
 Then something grabbed his hair, and he was surging upwards, breaking through the water

